narration_text: #C C picks box of #unsure with right hand
#C C holds packet of #unsure in left hand
#C C carries both packets towards kitchen sink
#C C places the packet in right hand on the sink
#C C shifts packet in left hand to right hand
#C C places the packet on the sink
#C C holds a thermos on gas cooker with right hand
#C C moves packet of #unsure in left hand off the sink
#C C moves right hand off the thermos
#C C pushes plate on chopping board in the sink with right hand
#C C stretches right hand towards thermos
#C C places packet of #unsure in left hand on the chopping board
#C C picks thermos with right hand
#C C places thermos in right hand on the board
#C C stretches right hand towards spoon on the sink
#C C picks the spoon
#C C wipes spoon with left hand
#C C picks the packet on the board with both hands
#C C opens the packet
#C C rotates the packet
#C C opens the packet
#C C scoops #unsure from the packet with spoon in right hand
#C C pours #unsure into thermos
#C C scoops again
#C C pours #unsure into thermos
#C C shakes the packet with left hand
#C C closes the packet with both hands
#C C walks towards fridge in the room
#C C shifts the packet from left to right hand
#C C places the packet on top of the fridge
#C C walks back to the sink
#C C picks packet of #unsure from the sink with right hand
#C C shifts the packet from right to left hand
#C C places spoon in right hand on the sink
#C C opens the packet with both hands
#C C stretches the packet towards thermos
#C C pours #unsure from the packet into thermos
